= Commands, Save Slots, and Debugging =

== Story Commands ==
Common command groups:
* ''/story list''
* ''/story info <story_id>''
* ''/story start <story_id>''
* ''/story stop [story_id]''
* ''/story pause <story_id>''
* ''/story progress''
* ''/story reload [story_id]''
* ''/story choose <choice_index> <node_id> <story_id>''

== Flag Commands ==
* ''/story flag set <story_id> <flag>''
* ''/story flag check <story_id> <flag>''

== Save Slot Commands ==
* ''/story slot list <story_id>''
* ''/story slot select <slot_id> <story_id>''
* ''/story slot new <slot_id> <story_id>''
* ''/story slot delete <slot_id> <story_id>''
* ''/story slot copy <from_slot> <to_slot> <story_id>''
* ''/story slot rename <slot_id> <story_id> <name>''

== Scene/Debug Utilities ==
* ''/story scene fade_in|fade_out|vignette|darkness|blur|cinematic_bars|chapter_start|screenshake''
* ''/story debug''
* ''/story mingui''
* ''/story overlay on|off''
* ''/story edit ...'' (runtime story editor/debug workflow)

== Save Slot Model ==
* Slots are per-player, per-story.
* Active slot determines where progress is read/written.
* Slot metadata includes name, last-played, and progress.

== Debugging Tips ==
* Use ''/story info'' to verify node structure.
* Use ''/story progress'' to inspect active state quickly.
* Use scene commands to validate cinematic effect tuning.

